Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:04.60,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nakasaki, I heard you just had a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.27,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, where did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.03,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it male or female?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.21,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.12,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.61,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.65,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Girls become independent \Nearlier than boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.87,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before she \Nstops listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.87,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That won't happen with Fuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:25.12,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I will raise her to be the \Nbiggest father lover in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:27.07,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.13,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.59,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't accept this much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.53,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.79,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I only spend money on fine women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:40.05,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let her drink the finest \Nmilk you can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.74,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.90,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,The Man's Household Situation \Nis Hard, His Heart is Soft
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.24,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:25.40,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Wash my underwear \Nseparately from Father's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.41,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.92,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wash them again myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:31.30,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.40,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.17,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.69,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash that again at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:42.51,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Are you the new maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.55,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:48.06,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ichihara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.31,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ichihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.58,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.06,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato? Etsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.81,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Etsuko, it's Ezurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.69,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.82,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Zura, it's Ezurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.03,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.94,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.33,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Do my laundry separate from Kuriko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.55,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure we don't \Neat at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.31,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Zura, it's Ezurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.92,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just listen to \Nmy daughter. Got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.25,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ezurako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.90,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Ezurako, it's Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.58,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.18,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I made a mistake. It's Ezurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.81,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.10,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.12,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The police commissioner, \NKatakuriko Matsudaira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.06,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The man who is known as the Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.53,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to those who wish to \Ndisrupt the order of Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.22,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest foe of the Joi patriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.16,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,In an attempt to uncover a scandal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.69,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working undercover \Nat his home for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:43.82,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,My focus has shifted away from my \Ninability to learn anything useful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.75,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,to this peculiar loneliness I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.70,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what it means to be a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.71,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,If so, what is a father? What is a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:58.59,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he fight for? Who \Nis he trying to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.93,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.43,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ezurako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.68,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.15,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,After working as a maid for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.56,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I've picked up this \Nhabit of eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.27,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,You also picked up the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.42,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me know if \NI'm being a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:26.53,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I also have a graffiti version \Nand a mental AT Field version.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.98,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Please get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.83,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,You're making too much noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.18,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:36.33,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about yelling at you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.29,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.88,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I said to get rid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.34,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could fool me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.34,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, to make up for earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.08,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,some of my friends booked
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.72,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Hills tomorrow \Nfor my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.23,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.26,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.96,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, will your father also be coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.94,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I would never invite him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.75,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he wouldn't come if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.48,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,His birthday is very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:10.11,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll celebrate it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.50,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,at the usual place with all those women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.11,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:20.75,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,He uses his work as an excuse \Nto avoid facing his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:26.76,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to call that coward my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.85,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.52,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,I am starting to feel concern \Nfor my greatest foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:40.27,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because Matsudaira's daughter \Nwas a nicer girl than I expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.49,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Or because I didn't want \Nto think that I've been
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:47.03,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,crossing swords with a man who \Ncan't control his own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.91,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.88,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuriko's birthday \Nparty is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.66,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be sleeping out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.66,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm gonna hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.79,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuriko wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.25,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Kuriko's \Nbirthday party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.42,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.43,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make her happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.72,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to teach her how men
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:17.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,are foolish, weak, and underhanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.69,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your duty as a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:23.09,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ezurako-san, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.73,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you walking \Naround with that board?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.43,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Nakasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.57,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I like a maid who's willing \Nto speak her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:36.63,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not much of a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.95,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Young people think \Nthat men grow wiser as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.54,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,they get older, but it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.63,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just as stupid as I always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:51.15,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Still the same old shy kid who \Ncan't bring myself to look
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:55.60,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,my precious daughter in the face, \Nor even talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.23,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.60,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I was becoming more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:05.61,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The man spoke openly \Nof his own foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.82,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Was he a big shot, or just an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.91,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}F-Forgive me, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.91,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Crafty or innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:17.12,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And I was most confused \Nby my own behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.06,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.33,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be dressed \Nformally for this affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.71,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.84,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um, only the left side \Nis dressed formally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.84,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,And that's just a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.77,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you have a problem \Nwith me wearing a tuxedo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.35,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I also brought a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.34,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.31,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're not supposed to let \Nanyone suspicious in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.48,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,What about me would be \Nconsidered suspicious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.31,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.07,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insult me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.79,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Are celebrities so special?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.66,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Your birthday party's probably \Nnothing more than an **gy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.57,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say such a hateful thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:58.00,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,A sinful gathering where you wear masks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:02.34,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,and put things on your sticks,\Nand shove them into...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.58,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a cheese fondue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.50,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that so loudly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.71,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:11.23,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's \Nhaving naughty thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.37,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,about a cheese fondue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.15,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.75,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.85,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nakasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.86,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here in place of the commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.83,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,So he isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.04,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Ezurako-san! Nakasaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.36,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.39,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.11,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.97,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:43.75,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.54,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did the system malfunction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.04,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.05,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.51,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call from Kuriko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.92,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.56,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Katakuriko Matsudaira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.52,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter's life is in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.31,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,The Blues Crew has taken \Ncontrol of Greater Edo Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.38,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your daughter's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.32,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll listen to our demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.05,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.72,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is somebody in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:21.63,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. It sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.71,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you let a man \Ntake a dump in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.25,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:35.99,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.51,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The commissioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.77,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,So he did come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.99,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.51,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it, Ezurako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.99,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I won't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.67,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where are you going, Commissioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.06,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,That was no longer the frail back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.91,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,of an old man washing underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:10.40,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,That was the stalwart back \Nof the Destroyer we feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.73,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The hostages include the children of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.89,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,various Bakufu officials \Nalong with Kuriko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.70,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Blues Crew must have learned about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.06,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,this party and planned the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:27.34,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that some of \Ntheir members were arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.63,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,for plotting to assassinate the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.63,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're demanding that \Nthose members be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.82,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And they also want the boss's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.10,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't agree to their demands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.57,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,they'll start killing a \Nhostage every thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.88,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go negotiate and \Ntry to buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.98,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,You guys need to find a way inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:46.66,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.16,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,And Yamazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.06,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,did you get a hold of the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:52.54,Main01,Yamazaki,0000,0000,0000,,His phone's been busy the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.42,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.67,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.18,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Ane-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.55,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.98,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to join you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.88,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right now? I'm in a duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:09.58,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't change careers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.50,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm devoted to you, Ane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.84,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I got another call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,My men are so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.16,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.82,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he finally answered the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.69,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Commissioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:26.16,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did you \Ncall me, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:30.66,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call my phone when \NI'm in terrorist territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.50,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrorizing my \Nconversation with Ane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.02,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to talk when you're
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.67,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,calling female escorts while \Nsneaking up on terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.26,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I was just settling matters \Nso the women left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,in this cruel world don't grieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.77,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,When a man dies, everyone \Nshould be wearing pure white.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.25,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I have fifty more girls \Nto call, so hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.03,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to clean up your act!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:50.98,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is completely black!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:54.63,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Hijikata-san and the other men \Nwill be entering the building soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.32,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.26,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't wait for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:11:59.99,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ezurako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.78,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,They've taken over the security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.76,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy to \Napproach the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.80,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then we shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:12.02,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I put something in this \Ncar to jam their radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.97,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And I did the same thing \Nto Matsudaira's present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.54,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.37,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to be acquainted \Nwith Edo's top tinkerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.64,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,In three hours, they'll \Nbegin executing hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:33.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I need to end \Ntheir lives before they end mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.08,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.04,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ezurako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.36,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't be able to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,by recklessly wandering around alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.02,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.72,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.91,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're no ordinary maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.91,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an ordinary maid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.68,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,who enjoys eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.42,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,How are negotiations going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.92,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a day to secure \Nthe release of our brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.36,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,They're obviously trying to buy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.32,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.84,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't giving them any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.68,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.12,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:13.85,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them that Matsudaira's \Nlife is already ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.76,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,though, technically, we still have to go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,through the formality \Nof taking it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.15,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect him to sneak in \Nby himself to save his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.10,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,H-He won't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:28.45,Main01,Kuriko,0000,0000,0000,,He would never try to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.58,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss. You'll \Nbe seeing him real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.38,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have him tied \Nup with a red ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.00,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. They're holed up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.09,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,main control room on the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.53,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the 9th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.13,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Every floor from the 10th \Nup is packed with guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.67,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this marker \Non the 9th floor is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.78,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you use this symbol for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:53.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.17,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,That's the tip of an ice cream cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:59.40,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And the three markers on \Nthe 10th floor are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.89,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they get cones when I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.78,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you wouldn't be \Nable to tell friend from foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.41,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a cone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.37,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I love to suck the last bit of ice \Ncream out of the end of a cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.81,Main01,Katsura,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll put corn in your poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.14,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I said cone, not corn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.66,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,And you said poop. You just \Nadmitted that it's poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.31,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, does it really matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.32,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you need to avoid those
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.70,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,ice cream cones as you make \Nyour way to the 50th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.67,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:29.13,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The tip of the ice cream is \Ntipping left and right, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.71,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The tip indicates the \Ndirection they're facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:35.01,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,When the three tips are tipping \Nin the same direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.57,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,you should tip past them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.96,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's too complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:43.17,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to use \Nthe word tip so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.57,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.94,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's an ice cream cone coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.70,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's tipping like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.95,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.80,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,10th floor... He didn't get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.16,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Has he noticed that the \Ncommissioner's on the 9th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.20,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Hide quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.21,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:14:59.96,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.95,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.96,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The ice cream cone split in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.00,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,A guy ran off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.99,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,But the ice cream's \Nstill in the elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.49,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,He just pooped his pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:16.10,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, both people and poop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.17,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,are registered under \Nthe ice cream marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.83,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why is poop even registered \Non your scanner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.77,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,And why am I not registered as a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.25,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He took the elevator \Ndown to find a bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:30.28,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,but he couldn't hold it \Nin and had to sparking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.28,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.58,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The cone is becoming wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.46,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Is he wiping his ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.53,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's probably crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:42.11,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I thought that there were \Nonly enemies above you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.63,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly poop up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.17,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer tell which \Nare human and which are poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.50,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,When I blew up that bathroom,\NI probably burst the water main.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.89,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,They can no longer take \Ncare of their business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.68,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this is too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.30,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,However, we can use this \Nsituation to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.06,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.40,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.11,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,They're all running down in \Nsearch of clean restrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.15,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,They really need to take a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.78,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,They're using the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.02,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance to \Ntake the elevator up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.16,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.76,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The wet cone is racing to the \Nelevator at a crazy speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.36,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did he notice the commissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.81,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,No, now that he's calmed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.21,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,he's returning for his underwear \Nso he can destroy the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.17,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Matsudaira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.17,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.40,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.64,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He's hanging on to the \Nbottom of the elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.34,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He is dedicated to his underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.37,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He really doesn't want \Nanyone to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.22,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Commissioner! The cone is below you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.56,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,And which one is the commissioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:50.06,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The cone is using the pointy \Nedge to try to break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.28,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what pointy edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.23,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a marker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.03,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.84,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He penetrated the poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.53,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that the commissioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.45,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it the poop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.70,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.71,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to drag Matsudaira off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.05,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Saved at the last second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.09,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.41,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,How can poop save him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.80,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Is that actually Matsudaira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.12,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The cone con finally \Ncornered himself and fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.43,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why was he trying so hard to protect \Na pair of dirty underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.18,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.77,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The Ice Cream Gang has noticed \Nthat something is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.36,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,When he makes it to the \Ntop, he'll be gunned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.84,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,They split up! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.11,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are two turds \Nmoving around independently?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.09,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to draw their attention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,so Matsudaira can make it to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.87,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a pair of \Nunderwear with poop on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.02,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,How did it turn into the \Ncommissioner's partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:44.93,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.37,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Ice Cream Gang is ignoring the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,underwear and gathering \Non the 50th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.71,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,No shit, Sherlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.44,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.39,Main01,Hijikata,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.35,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The ice cream cones are disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.36,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,This poop was actually the diversion...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.79,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:31.05,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,He really took out all of \Nthe terrorists by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's one cone left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.64,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.31,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your precious underwear \Nand squad are all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.44,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.44,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,No one will know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:57.44,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,You're placing your duty as a \Ncop over your duty as a father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.51,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't call yourself a father
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.82,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't mind your daughter \Nbeing used as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.35,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't even call \Nyourself a man if you let
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.47,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,someone who hurt your daughter \Nwalk away unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.96,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,A father's duty isn't much to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.96,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Kids are raised fine by their mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:22.79,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm bringing in \Nmoney, I have no other use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:27.90,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to praise her \Nwhen she does something good,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.20,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,and scold her when she \Ndoes something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.73,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:38.16,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,This fist represents my duty \Nas a police commissioner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:42.36,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,and a lousy Edo dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.30,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:46.87,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.12,Main01,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,My underwear is still around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:54.19,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,The decoy was my own underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.13,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I have one thing to say \Nto you as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.26,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wash your own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.01,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,shitty underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.98,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.44,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,This was your chance to \Nscore some points with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.66,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,She won't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.91,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with playing \Nthe role of a lousy dad
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.03,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,since it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.91,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.44,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:35.54,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I found it when I was cleaning \Nyour daughter's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:42.59,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably going to give \Nit to you if you showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.59,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday Father
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.00,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I left your present in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:50.44,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,How is that supposed \Nto make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:54.22,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,A maid who goes into my daughter's \Nroom without permission
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:56.36,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,gets fired on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.39,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nakasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:57.86,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:01.11,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Dump this rotten maid in a ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.59,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.43,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dump the maid in a ditch \Nwhere the police won't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.46,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop yapping and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:07.87,Main01,Nakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.12,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet, you'll \Nmeet more than my fist, Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.87,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.38,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The police commissioner, \NKatakuriko Matsudaira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.88,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Matsudaira
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:24.88,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest foe of the Joi patriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.38,Main01,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop that, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.69,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he doesn't \Nfeel welcome in his own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.69,Main01,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can do the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.73,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,The world is his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:33.87,Main01,Matsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Forget it. I'll do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.85,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,And so he goes off to work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.85,Main01,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, Miss Kuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.90,Main01,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lovely hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:42.23,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have seen on display
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:47.54,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,the bond between father and daughter \Nas they stand back to back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:52.41,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the dignity of \Na so-called lousy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.55,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,Katakuriko Matsudaira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.34,Main01,Zura,0000,0000,0000,,You make a fitting opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.89,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode: Blue and Red Ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:31.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Blue and Red Ecstasy.
